Use the standard library
This is how to simplify of x and n:
   Remember that a is quotient of (tofloat of x) and (tofloat of n)
   Remember that b is quotient of (tofloat of n) and (tofloat of x)
   When a is 1.000000, then:
      The answer is 1
   But, if not:
      When b is 1.000000, then:
         The answer is 1
      But, if not:
         The answer is 0
      End when
   End when
